<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmatu śakavarṣaṁbulu 1221 Agunēṭi 
<lb n="2"/>vikāri saṁva<unclear>tsa</unclear>ra nija Āṣāḍha śu 15 ma nāṁṭi sō 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>magrahaṇamunāṁḍu svasti śrīmatu viṣṇuvarddha 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>na dēva cakravarttulunu Ā rudradēvaniṁgārunu ta <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>svasti śrīmatu sarvvalōkāśrayalaina <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> vallabhacakra 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>varttulakunu tama talli bācadēvigā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> gārikiṁ buṇyamu 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>gānu mācaya <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> riki vinnapamu sēsi cēyiṁcina 
<lb n="8"/>dharmmamu tama <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> pūUmuladēva <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> nu 
<lb n="9" break="no"/><unclear>pa</unclear>sulaku tamanibayati polamuna pullari <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> vāri kānike 
<lb n="10"/>nu nā <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> vritti <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> gala ciṁtatāḍu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="11"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> mu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> kuṁṭa <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> nu nuṁ ciṁtaceṭlu 
<lb n="12"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> mācaṁdrārkkasthāyigānu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svadattā dviguṇaṁ 
<lb n="13"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> rēṇa svadattaṁ ni 
<lb n="14-15"/><ce>lines are damaged</ce> 
</p>

